title: Suni Lee, Chelsea Bid, Alyssa Nakken
itunes:title: Suni Lee, Chelsea Bid, Alyssa Nakken
description:
On Wednesday's Business of Sports, Michael Barr, Scarlet Fu and Mike Lynch discuss the rising interest and viewership in gymnastics as Olympic gold medalist, Suni Lee shines on the collegiate level, the owner of the Boston Celtics teaming up with Larry Tanenbaum and John Terry to bid for Chelsea, and San Francisco Giants' Alyssa Nakken becoming the first female to coach on field.


See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
